name: Jabra Evolve 65t MS - True wireless earphones with mic - in-ear - Bluetooth - titanium black | Dell USA
description: The Jabra Evolve 65t is engineered to be the world's first UC-certified true wireless earbuds. Designed for business professionals, enjoy Skype for Business and UC-certified sound with 4-microphone technology. Take calls from your smartphone, or plug in the USB adaptor to your PC or laptop and take calls from your softphone. With up to 15 hours of battery, Passive Noise Cancellation, and third-generation true wireless technology, the Evolve 65t ensures that your calls last the day, block out disruptive background noise, and avoid audio dropouts.
